  "detailed_description": "Falling from the roof of a skyscraper, climb perilous mountains, blaze through industrial landscapes, each of which poses a new challenge and provides the opportunity to perform wild stunts on your dirt bike. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1913610/extras/0589398af032a9e2cee268615ef6abbc.poster.avif?t=1770428188\" width=618 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1913610/extras/0589398af032a9e2cee268615ef6abbc.webm?t=1770428188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1913610/extras/0589398af032a9e2cee268615ef6abbc.mp4?t=1770428188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Game Features:<br><br>1. Over 80 levels.<br>2. The motorbike controls are realistic and easy to pick up. You can perform some amazing jumps and flips.<br>3. You can complete some classic action stunts, including falling from the roof of a skyscraper, leaping over a valley on a motorcycle, driving through the glass wall of a building, etc.<br>4. With various bike types and enhanced features.<br><br>Complete the challenge like a stunt star. Try out the many stunt jump opportunities to collect award.",
